flowchart TD
  M[Pick a metric] --> C[Collect data]
  C --> T[Train model]
  T --> R1[Many labels are wrong → relabel]
  R1 --> T
  T --> R2[Poor on one class → collect more data]
  R2 --> C
  T --> R3[Too slow → make it smaller]
  R3 --> T
  T --> D[Deploy]
  D --> R4[Data shifts over time → retrain]
  R4 --> C
